_sText:
Hello! Here it is, the first RP map for CS:S for FPSBanana for you people of the community to get your hands on.
Before I get down to explainging this, I owe great credit to Natalya - Creator of RP Mod (CS:S) - http://www.lady-natalya.info/index.php - Also credit to f.kalkman - Orgins of map.
But yeah.. All original content to him.
This great map contains the following and more,
-Petrol station
-Park/Playground.
-Flasts, multiple rooms - Lockable.
-Custom materials & models.. Everywhere.
-Cafe/Restaraunt.
-Cinema. - Working.
-Gym/Workout.
-Gunshop. - Realistic, to a exstent.
-Police station W/Riotsheilds.
Disarming jail cells.

-Toilates
-Tools shop.
-Tech shop/Computing.
-Mayors office, requires code.
-Hospital.
-Overall, all features of a small street.

Took about a month to complete. With help from multiple others.. As listed in credit section.
Very important if your going to use this, it also could be used for a DM Map, would be fun..
You must add this to your server.cfg.. 
"net_maxfilesize 25"
The defult is not large enough. #30 would be a good value to put it at.
There may be a video coming soon, if anyone can make one feel free to.
Works very well, no known bugs.. 
Skybox may be slightly glitchie but that depends on your PC/hardware.
I belive that is all. 
Hope you enjoy this map and have fun.
